Gaupol 0.12.1
=============

 [D] Fix text correction assistant's capitalization task
 [D] Fix remaining NameErrors with function arguments (#10034)


Gaupol 0.13
===========

 * Migrate to (Py)GTK 2.12
    - gtk.AboutDialog: "name" replaced with "program-name"
    - gtk.Builder: Build an interface from an XML UI definition
    - gtk.RecentAction: New class for recent-files menu items
    - gtk.Tooltip: New API that allows complex tooltips


